<h3>Payments</h3>
<br/>
<div id="items">
  <div class="one_third">
    <div style="margin-bottom: 30px;" class="box_heading"><h2 style="top: 8px;">Overview</h2><span class="line"></span>
    </div>
    <div id="sponsors">
      <p>Total fees for the trip are <%= number_to_currency(@registration.total_amount) %> and is due in full by March 14th 2017. To help make the payments
        less painful we break them up into installments.</p>
        <span style="font-weight:bold;color:black;">Payment schedule:</span>
      <ul>
        <li style="width:95px;">Due Date</li>
        <li style="width:70px;">Student</li>
        <li class="last" style="width:70px;<% unless current_user.chaperone %> opacity: 0.5;<% end %>">Chaperone</li>
        <% @schedule.each do |pmt| %>
            <li style="width:95px;"><%= pmt[:date].strftime("%m/%d/%Y") %></li>
            <li style="width:70px;"><%= number_to_currency(pmt[:student]) %></li>
            <li class="last" style="width:70px;<% unless current_user.chaperone %> opacity: 0.5;<% end %>"><%= number_to_currency(pmt[:chaperone]) %></li>
        <% end %>
      </ul>
      <p>
        <% if @registration.grade == 5 %>
            If necessary, on 5/26/2017, an extra payment of <strong>#300-$500 for students</strong> and <strong>$600-$800 for chaperones</strong> may be needed.
        <% end %>
        <% if @registration.grade == 8 %>
            If necessary, on 4/6/2017, an extra payment of <strong>#200-$500 for students</strong> and <strong>$400-$800 for chaperones</strong> may be needed.
        <% end %>
        This may change based on airfare (the most expensive part of the trip), exchange rates and our fund raising plus scrip credits â€“ so buy scrip!
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="one_third">
    <div style="margin-bottom: 30px;" class="box_heading"><h2 style="top: 8px;">Payment</h2><span class="line"></span>
    </div>
    <div class="events">
      <ul>
        <li style="border-bottom: none;">
          <div class="date"><span><%= @registration.next_pmt_date.day %></span><%= @registration.next_pmt_date.strftime("%b") %></div>
          <div class="details">
            <h5 style="margin-bottom:0;">Upcoming Payment</h5>
            <p>Status:
              <% if @registration.total_due > 0 %>
                  <span style="color:red;">Payment Due</span>
              <% else %>
                  <span style="color:green;">Current</span>
              <% end %>
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <form action="https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr" method="post">
              <input type="hidden" name="cmd" value="_cart">
              <input type="hidden" name="upload" value="1">
              <input type="hidden" name="business" value="kathy.black@pdx.edu">
              <input type="hidden" name="currency_code" value="USD">
              <input type="hidden" name="notify_url" value="<%= payments_receipt_url %>">
              <input type="hidden" name="shopping_url" value="<%= payments_overview_url %>">
              <input type="hidden" name="invoice" value="<%= @registration.id %>-<%= (@registration.payments.length + 1) %>-<%= Time.now.to_i %>">
              <input type="hidden" name="item_name_1" value="<%= @registration.sfname %> <%= @registration.slname %> - <%= @registration.grade %>th Grade Trip">
              <input type="hidden" name="item_number_1" value="<%= @registration.next_pmt_date.strftime("%m/%d/%Y") %> <%= @registration.user.chaperone ? "Chaperone" : "Student" %> Payment">
              <input type="hidden" name="quantity_1" value="1">
              $<input style="width:135px;height:30px;padding-left:5px;margin-top:20px;" type="text" name="amount_1" value="<%= @registration.total_due %>"><br/>
              <input type="image" name="submit" style="margin-top: 10px;"
                     src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/webstatic/en_US/btn/btn_checkout_pp_142x27.png" alt="PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online">
            </form>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p style="margin-bottom:5px;"><span style="font-weight:bold;color:black;">Payment Due:</span>  <%= number_to_currency(@registration.total_due) %></p>
      <p style="margin-bottom:5px;"><span style="font-weight:bold;color:black;">Payments Made:</span> <%= number_to_currency(@registration.total_paid) %></p>
      <% if @registration.scholarship > 0 %>
        <p style="margin-bottom:5px;"><span style="font-weight:bold;color:black;">Scholarships:</span> <%= number_to_currency(@registration.scholarship) %></p>
      <% end %>
      <p style="margin-bottom:5px;"><span style="font-weight:bold;color:black;">Payoff Amount:</span> <%= number_to_currency(@registration.payoff_amount) %></p>
      <p style="margin-bottom:10px;"><span style="font-weight:bold;color:black;">Total Amount:</span> <%= number_to_currency(@registration.total_amount) %></p>
      <p>
        If you can not make a full payment this pay period, then pay what you can.  Make the rest up as soon as you can.
        If you would like to pay ahead or make your payment in full then feel free to do so.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="one_third column_last">
    <div style="margin-bottom: 30px;" class="box_heading"><h2 style="top: 8px;">History</h2><span class="line"></span></div>
    <div class="news">
      <ul>
        <% @registration.payments.each do |pmt| %>
            <li style="margin-bottom:5px;padding-bottom:5px;"><h5 style="margin-bottom:0px;"><%= number_to_currency(pmt.amount) %> - <%= pmt.pmtdate.strftime("%b #{pmt.pmtdate.day.ordinalize}, %Y") %></h5>
              <p style="font-size: .9em;">
                Payment: <%= pmt.pmtnum %><br/>
                Logged on: <%= pmt.pmtdate.strftime("%m/%d/%Y %T") %>
              </p>
            </li>
        <% end %>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="clear"></div>
</div>